regen.absent_element: action when a new job is added while another is running
regen.new_specification: The system shall recalculate pass values and re-evaluate scheduling priority upon new job insertion.

regen.absent_element: dynamic time-slicing between all jobs currently running
regen.new_specification: The scheduler shall dynamically adjust time slices between all running jobs to optimize resource utilization and ensure fair execution.
The scheduler shall determine and adjust time slices for each job executed based on stride values to ensure efficiency.
